00:54:42,070 --> 00:54:44,072
Go home and get a present at home.

771
00:54:44,781 --> 00:54:47,075
-A present?
-You'll find it at home.

772
00:54:48,493 --> 00:54:51,538
To do that, what do you need to do?

773
00:54:54,791 --> 00:54:56,793
Beep.

774
00:55:01,673 --> 00:55:03,758
How do you keep his job as a director?

775
00:55:04,175 --> 00:55:06,344
Can you lead a normal life like this?

776
00:55:21,067 --> 00:55:22,569
-Bye.
-Take care.

777
00:55:32,912 --> 00:55:35,832
I want to be happy even if I'm exhausted.

778
00:55:36,708 --> 00:55:39,669
I'm exhausted, but I'm happy.

779
00:55:40,795 --> 00:55:44,132
At least today was a complete success.

780
00:55:46,718 --> 00:55:47,969
Isn't it more tiring to play?

781
00:55:48,970 --> 00:55:50,221
Not really.

782
00:55:50,805 --> 00:55:52,515
Right. It's just something people say.

783
00:55:52,599 --> 00:55:55,310
Right. I prefer playing
to working. Always.

784
00:55:57,103 --> 00:55:58,605
It's time for us to go back home.

785
00:55:58,688 --> 00:56:01,107
It's time to find something
we wanted to find during the trip.

786
00:56:02,192 --> 00:56:03,777
Well, it was a short trip.

787
00:56:03,860 --> 00:56:05,779
Don't be disappointed
even if you don't find anything.

788
00:56:06,279 --> 00:56:07,113
What?

789
00:56:07,197 --> 00:56:08,823
But I've already found it.

790
00:56:08,907 --> 00:56:10,158
-Really?
-Yes.

791
00:56:13,078 --> 00:56:15,246
Here's the back I was looking for.

792
00:56:17,916 --> 00:56:19,292
You definitely found it.

793
00:56:20,043 --> 00:56:21,169
This is free, right?

794
00:56:21,252 --> 00:56:23,046
-The back you're hugging?
-Yes.

795
00:56:24,380 --> 00:56:25,882
It's not free.

796
00:56:26,633 --> 00:56:28,718
I can actually pay you a premium for it.

797
00:56:30,345 --> 00:56:32,180
Don't change.

798
00:56:33,181 --> 00:56:34,182
I won't.

799
00:56:36,101 --> 00:56:37,143
Promise me.

800
00:56:38,186 --> 00:56:41,022
I found something, too.
I saw a different side of you.

801
00:56:41,272 --> 00:56:42,398
Promise me.

802
00:56:42,482 --> 00:56:43,858
I'll do it,

803
00:56:44,359 --> 00:56:46,194
but I didn't know
you believed in these promises.

804
00:56:46,736 --> 00:56:49,864
I want to believe it just for today.
Stop talking and promise me.

805
00:56:54,077 --> 00:56:55,245
Stamp and seal.

806
00:57:03,294 --> 00:57:05,255
Gosh, it's really okay.

807
00:57:06,089 --> 00:57:08,091
It's late. Besides, you worked hard today.

808
00:57:08,174 --> 00:57:09,259
Work hard?

809
00:57:09,425 --> 00:57:11,052
I had so much fun today.

810
00:57:11,219 --> 00:57:12,262
Is that so?

811
00:57:13,054 --> 00:57:14,722
I'll drop you off at the main road.

812
00:57:14,806 --> 00:57:16,975
Ha-yun might see me dropping you off.

813
00:57:19,310 --> 00:57:21,229
I'm sorry
about the text message that night.

814
00:57:21,312 --> 00:57:22,730
Gosh, don't even say that.

815
00:57:22,897 --> 00:57:25,275
Actually,
I even thought about apologizing to you.

816
00:57:25,358 --> 00:57:26,985
Gosh, don't even say that.

817
00:57:27,819 --> 00:57:30,822
That's my point.
Something felt weird about that.

818
00:57:31,739 --> 00:57:33,825
Never blame Ha-yun for it.

819
00:57:33,992 --> 00:57:35,618
Women might feel insure about that.

820
00:57:35,743 --> 00:57:37,912
She doesn't need
to feel insure now, anyway.

821
00:57:38,955 --> 00:57:41,166
Ha-yun was sorry about
what she did to you.

822
00:57:42,167 --> 00:57:44,127
She's not that...

823
00:57:45,920 --> 00:57:47,672
I want to say she's not that rude,

824
00:57:48,631 --> 00:57:51,718
but she had already been so rude to you.
So this is a bit...

825
00:57:58,141 --> 00:57:59,225
You hate her, right?

826
00:58:00,685 --> 00:58:01,728
Pardon?

827
00:58:01,978 --> 00:58:03,188
I'm talking about Ha-yun.

828
00:58:04,981 --> 00:58:08,151
You'll still be upset
even if she apologizes to you.

829
00:58:09,736 --> 00:58:12,280
She behaved in a way
you couldn't understand.

830
00:58:12,822 --> 00:58:15,158
And as you still don't understand
why she behaved that way,

831
00:58:15,241 --> 00:58:16,743
how could you not be angry?

832
00:58:18,995 --> 00:58:20,330
That's everyone.

833
00:58:20,705 --> 00:58:23,500
You hate it.
Of course, that's only natural.

834
00:58:25,084 --> 00:58:27,712
You should pluck up your courage
at a time like that.

835
00:58:28,963 --> 00:58:30,423
The courage not to hate.

836
00:58:30,840 --> 00:58:32,300
"The courage not to hate"?

837
00:58:32,383 --> 00:58:35,929
It turns out you need nothing
but courage to achieve that.

838
00:58:36,221 --> 00:58:37,347
Try it.

839
00:58:38,515 --> 00:58:42,310
Love is more valuable than hatred.

840
00:58:57,867 --> 00:58:59,327
Who were you with?

841
00:59:01,746 --> 00:59:04,374
Never mind. I'm sorry.

842
00:59:29,315 --> 00:59:30,608
What did you do today?

843
00:59:33,945 --> 00:59:35,238
I waited for you.

844
00:59:47,333 --> 00:59:48,334
I'm sorry.

845
00:59:49,502 --> 00:59:50,670
I'm late.

846
01:00:41,846 --> 01:00:43,014
You must be tired.

847
01:01:00,990 --> 01:01:02,408
When you say yes.

848
01:01:03,284 --> 01:01:06,079
I've been recording us very diligently.

849
01:01:06,162 --> 01:01:08,081
I take photos and write things.

850
01:01:08,164 --> 01:01:09,165
Look.

851
01:01:09,415 --> 01:01:10,249
This is

852
01:01:11,125 --> 01:01:13,336
an app where I can take photos
and leave short memos.

853
01:01:13,419 --> 01:01:15,421
It's in private for now,

854
01:01:15,546 --> 01:01:18,299
but I'll open it when we get married.

855
01:01:18,841 --> 01:01:20,385
When you say "Yes, I will."

856
01:01:53,251 --> 01:01:54,419
ONE-LINE JOURNAL

857
01:02:05,638 --> 01:02:07,598
EUN-JEONG, HONG-DAE

858
01:02:07,682 --> 01:02:12,019
This is the first photo we took together,
but you don't like this photo.

859
01:02:12,812 --> 01:02:13,813
I'm sorry.

860
01:02:14,647 --> 01:02:16,607
I'll put my head closer
to the camera next time.

861
01:02:17,817 --> 01:02:19,986
As it's our first photo,
it gives me butterflies.

862
01:02:20,945 --> 01:02:23,197
As time passes by
and reaches our exciting future,

863
01:02:24,282 --> 01:02:25,867
let's look at these photos while smiling.

864
01:02:27,243 --> 01:02:29,454
Well... Let's just say that I want

865
01:02:30,246 --> 01:02:31,831
a taste of being cool, too.

866
01:02:37,086 --> 01:02:38,337
They say no.

867
01:02:39,046 --> 01:02:40,089
Let's go.

868
01:02:40,465 --> 01:02:41,591
Get lost!

869
01:02:45,928 --> 01:02:47,054
They're over there.

870
01:02:50,349 --> 01:02:51,601
It was like that from the start.

871
01:02:53,102 --> 01:02:55,188
"I want to stay with this girl a bit more.

872
01:02:55,271 --> 01:02:57,064
I want to talk to her a bit more."

873
01:02:57,940 --> 01:02:59,609
That's how I felt today as always.

874
01:03:00,067 --> 01:03:03,112
I felt really crappy, but I held it in.

875
01:03:04,447 --> 01:03:06,949
Gosh. I shouldn't have.

876
01:03:12,121 --> 01:03:15,333
Don't you think
something is going to happen?

877
01:03:17,960 --> 01:03:19,045
Like what?

878
01:03:21,088 --> 01:03:22,215
I don't know.

879
01:03:29,263 --> 01:03:30,431
Do you want to know?

880
01:03:34,852 --> 01:03:37,355
We kissed for the first time.

881
01:03:38,314 --> 01:03:42,068
I'll remember everything else.
You just remember this.

882
01:03:42,902 --> 01:03:45,488
You kissed me first.

883
01:03:57,625 --> 01:04:00,169
Today was the first time I saw you upset.

884
01:04:00,670 --> 01:04:03,756
I thought about being upset at you, too
for a brief moment,

885
01:04:04,507 --> 01:04:05,758
but I couldn't.

886
01:04:06,592 --> 01:04:08,177
Because you were too beautiful.

887
01:04:09,345 --> 01:04:12,598
What am I going to do?
I guess looks matter for me.

888
01:04:27,655 --> 01:04:29,282
I went to the hospital.

889
01:04:32,159 --> 01:04:33,286
I

890
01:04:35,162 --> 01:04:36,247
miss you.

891
01:04:43,087 --> 01:04:44,422
I WENT TO THE HOSPITAL

892
01:04:44,505 --> 01:04:45,840
I... MISS YOU

893
01:04:56,350 --> 01:04:58,728
The more I observe you,
the more reliable you are.

894
01:04:59,478 --> 01:05:01,063
I have no doubt

895
01:05:01,606 --> 01:05:04,233
that you will be brave even without me

896
01:05:07,570 --> 01:05:11,282
because you are the love of my life.

897
01:05:11,824 --> 01:05:14,368
I trust you. I do.

898
01:05:17,663 --> 01:05:18,748
I really do, but...

899
01:05:21,751 --> 01:05:24,670
Gosh, no. I don't.

900
01:05:39,185 --> 01:05:40,478
Please

901
01:05:42,104 --> 01:05:43,272
take care

902
01:05:44,482 --> 01:05:45,524
of yourself

903
01:05:47,526 --> 01:05:48,736
for me.

904
01:05:53,741 --> 01:05:54,909
I will.

905
01:05:56,702 --> 01:05:57,870
I'll do it.

906
01:06:01,666 --> 01:06:03,292
I'll make sure I do.

907
01:06:05,628 --> 01:06:06,796
I love you.

908
01:07:08,149 --> 01:07:09,900
I told you not to come to my work.

909
01:07:09,984 --> 01:07:11,610
Had you told me to come,
I wouldn't have come.

910
01:07:11,694 --> 01:07:13,529
You still don't know me.

911
01:07:14,196 --> 01:07:16,323
-Ms. Hwang!
-You want to take In-guk?

912
01:07:16,407 --> 01:07:18,200
How about we live together?

913
01:07:18,284 --> 01:07:20,369
To tell you the truth, I am...

914
01:07:20,453 --> 01:07:21,787
I can't let you go.

915
01:07:21,871 --> 01:07:24,498
-Delete them.
-What are you doing?

916
01:07:24,582 --> 01:07:26,250
Say, "Please delete them."

917
01:07:26,333 --> 01:07:28,210
-Come in.
-Just be nice to me.

918
01:07:28,294 --> 01:07:29,378
I don't need you to be shy.

919
01:07:29,462 --> 01:07:31,338
Why is he exchanging these photos
with you?

920
01:07:31,589 --> 01:07:33,674
Those photos were no big deal.
They were cute.

921
01:07:33,758 --> 01:07:35,217
Damn it.

922
01:07:35,426 --> 01:07:37,678
Do you know
that being nice actually suits you?

923
01:07:37,762 --> 01:07:39,513
-Thanks.
-For what?

924
01:07:39,597 --> 01:07:41,640
I don't know. Just thank you.

925
01:07:41,724 --> 01:07:43,642
Hey, it's not your fault.

926
01:07:43,726 --> 01:07:44,810
What are you talking about?

927
01:07:44,894 --> 01:07:47,813
I just want to switch the order
of Hwan-dong and your drama.

928
01:07:47,897 --> 01:07:49,190
It's your fault.

929
01:07:49,356 --> 01:07:51,192
You made her break her leg!
It's all your fault.

930
01:07:51,275 --> 01:07:52,568
I want to see you.

931
01:07:52,651 --> 01:07:54,278
But what can I do? It's our project.

932
01:07:54,361 --> 01:07:55,863
Does he think I have nothing to do?

933
01:07:55,946 --> 01:07:58,491
Damn it. That fool.

934
01:07:58,574 --> 01:08:00,284
I was crazy busy.

935
01:08:00,576 --> 01:08:01,786
That's an excuse.

936
01:08:01,952 --> 01:08:05,706
Gosh, you know that both of us are busy.
Why do you let this upset you?

937
01:08:06,415 --> 01:08:09,251
I'm going to be disappointed in you today.

938
01:08:10,461 --> 01:08:12,546
